name: Everything Must Go (Help Wanted)
description: Video documentation of a custom-programmed LED signage display by Jeffrey Michael Austin, originally intended to be part of a solo exhibition titled Everything Must Go in April 2020 which has since been indefinitely postponed due to complications caused by the COVID-19 pandemic. The physical work has already been acquired by a private collection, the owner of which has not been consulted regarding the separate sale of the workâ€™s video documentation as an NFT.
